               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18431023-name-553" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-553" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-553" type="surname" value="HART"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-553" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>MART HART</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the mother of Henry Hart. On the 2nd of Oct, about seven o'clock, I missed this bacon—Thompson brought it back—the prisoner came into the shop in the evening for an errand.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18431023-name-554" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-554" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-554" type="surname" value="THOMPSON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-554" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD THOMPSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a constable—I found the bacon in a frying-pan, by the side of the prisoner, in Harefield's brick-field, about a quarter of a mile from the prosecutor's, about half-past seven o'clock—there were two persons with him—he first said he bad not got the bacon, and at last he said he had got it, he had taken it away.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I did not say I took it, I knew nothing about it; another chap took it. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> The other man said nothing about it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18431023-name-555" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-555" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-555" type="surname" value="HART"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-555" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY HART</persName>
                  </hi>. I went home—I went with the constable, and found the bacon by the prisoner's side—he said he bad not taken it, and at last the others said, "Give it up."</p>
